---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Quality & Regulatory Compliance" currentPage="/services/quality-regulatory-compliance">
  <section class="hero-section">
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Quality & Regulatory Compliance</h1>
      <p>Navigate complex regulatory landscapes with confidence.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="content-main">
          <h2>Ensuring Compliance, Enabling Success</h2>
          <p>NovintiX provides comprehensive quality and regulatory consulting services to help life sciences companies meet the highest standards of compliance. Our experienced team understands the complexities of global regulatory requirements and helps you navigate them efficiently.</p>

          <h3>Our Services Include:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Quality Management Systems</strong> - QMS design, implementation, and optimization</li>
            <li><strong>Regulatory Strategy</strong> - Global regulatory planning and submission support</li>
            <li><strong>Audit Readiness</strong> - Preparation for FDA, EU MDR, and ISO audits</li>
            <li><strong>CAPA Management</strong> - Corrective and preventive action systems</li>
            <li><strong>Risk Management</strong> - ISO 14971 compliance and risk assessment</li>
            <li><strong>Post-Market Surveillance</strong> - Vigilance, complaint handling, and MDR reporting</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Regulatory Expertise</h3>
          <p>Our team has extensive experience with:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>FDA 21 CFR Part 820, 210/211</li>
            <li>EU MDR and IVDR</li>
            <li>ISO 13485 and ISO 9001</li>
            <li>Health Canada and international regulations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="content-sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h5>Related Services</h5>
            <ul>
              <li><a href="/services/clinical-affairs">Clinical Affairs</a></li>
              <li><a href="/services/manufacturing">Manufacturing</a></li>
              <li><a href="/services/product-engineering">Product Engineering</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h5>Get Started</h5>
            <p>Need help with compliance?</p>
            <a href="/contact-us" class="btn">Contact Us</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 350px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E2128 0%, #32353E 100%);
    padding: 7% 0;
  }

  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: url('/images/pattern.png') repeat;
    opacity: 0.1;
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 720px;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .hero-content h1 {
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .hero-content p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .content-section {
    padding: 5em 0;
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 50px;
  }

  .content-main h2 {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .content-main h3 {
    margin-top: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .content-main p {
    color: #7C7C7D;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .content-main ul {
    margin: 20px 0;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  .content-main li {
    color: #7C7C7D;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .content-main li strong {
    color: #1E2128;
  }

  .sidebar-card {
    background: #f8f8f9;
    border-radius: 15px;
    padding: 25px;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
  }

  .sidebar-card h5 {
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .sidebar-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .sidebar-card li {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .sidebar-card a {
    color: #033C59;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .sidebar-card a:hover {
    color: #F5A302;
  }

  .sidebar-card p {
    color: #7C7C7D;
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .sidebar-card .btn {
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
